data.description: Delightful 16 acre horse property with a detached car garage! It boasts an interior that captivates with its blend of wood-look and carpeted floors, vaulted ceilings illuminated by skylights, and a cozy living room anchored by a fireplace. Eat-in kitchen includes abundant cabinets, SS appliances, a breakfast bar, and a handy pantry. Retreat to the main bedroom, which offers a mirrored closet, a private route to a bonus room, and an ensuite with dual sinks and a soaking tub. Vast backyard is an oasis of opportunities, featuring a covered patio, a workshop, a shed, a play area, and plenty of space to develop as you wish. Get ready to be mesmerized by breathtaking sunset hues and majestic mountain vistas. Experience serenity and beauty combined in this tranquil gem.
